      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ad aifgabje to Israëka Behrnu Drandfe pa fa- weem Gahjumein no tahs Tuksnibas Sin/us ta KUN- GA Pauehleschanu/ un tee ap- mette to Lehgeri eekſch Rawidim/ un tur ne bija Uhdens preeſch teem Laudim ja-dserx."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad bahrahs tee Landisar Mohsu nn fazzija: Dohd mums Uhdeni / ka mehs dserxam; tad fazzija Mohsus us teem: ko juhs ar man barratees? kapehz kahr- dinajat juhs to KUNGII?"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu tee Laudis tur pehz Uhdeni flahpe / tad kurneja tee Laudis prett Mohsu/ un fazzija: kapehz tu tad muhs effi lizzis no Eajptes iseet / muhs un muhfus Behrnus/ un muhfus Lohpus noslahpeht?"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Mohsus kleedſe us to KUNGII/ un fazzija: Ko darri- ſchu es teem Laudim? ne dauds truhkſt/ tad tee mann ar Akmi- Neen nomehtahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGGS us Mohsu : Eij preeſch teem Akmini/ un litke to winna"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Reds/ es stahweſch Preekſcha tur us Oreba A Kalnu / un tev buhs us mint fist/ tad tētezzehs Uh ta/ ka teem Laudim irr jo un Mohsus darrija ta Israëta Wezzaju Azium."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nofauze Weetas Wahrdü Massa uriba/ Israëta Behrnu Ba nas deht/ un tapehz ka KUNGII bij kahrdinaſch daini: Irrag tas KUNGII tu Widdü/ jeb ne?"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nahze Amal kawahs ar Israëlu eekſ widim."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Moh Josuü: Islaſſi mums V un iſeij/ un taujees prett leku/ ribt es stahweſchn us kalna Gallu/ un tas Deen lis buhs manna Rohkâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad darrija Josuü Mohsus tam bij fazzija: wahs prett Amaleku / un fus/ un Aärongs un Urs ka ta Pakalna Gallu."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tamehr Moh was Rohkas pazehlis turre warreja Israëls / un wiꞥſch favu Rohku nola uswarreja Amaleks."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Mohsus Rohk finaggas / tad nehme tee"
    }
  ],
